description: A skill that will give you your fortune when you ask for it! Fortune cookies are nice but you can save yourself the calories and just ask Alexa to give you your fortune!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask fortune teller to give me my fortune
Alexa, ask fortune teller for my fortune
Alexa, ask fortune teller for a fortune
name: Fortune Teller
shortDescription: A skill that will give you your fortune when you ask for it!
